<span id="cb4-9"><a href="#cb4-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt;   data.sample_size data.country data.iso_code data.gid_0 data.survey_date</span></span>
<span id="cb4-10"><a href="#cb4-10" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 1             2396      Germany           DEU        DEU         20210501</span></span>
<span id="cb4-11"><a href="#cb4-11" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 2             2514      Germany           DEU        DEU         20210502</span></span>
<span id="cb4-12"><a href="#cb4-12" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 3             2318      Germany           DEU        DEU         20210503</span></span>
<span id="cb4-13"><a href="#cb4-13" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt;    status</span></span>
<span id="cb4-14"><a href="#cb4-14" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 1 success</span></span>
<span id="cb4-15"><a href="#cb4-15" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 2 success</span></span>
<span id="cb4-16"><a href="#cb4-16" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 3 success</span></span></code></pre></div>
<p>Again, we can also receive data for a specific region in a country.</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb5"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb5-1"><a href="#cb5-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">CTIS_open_data_region</span>(<span class="at">indicator =</span> <span class="st">&quot;vaccine_acpt&quot;</span>, </span>
<span id="cb5-2"><a href="#cb5-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                       <span class="at">type =</span> <span class="st">&quot;daily&quot;</span>, </span>
<span id="cb5-3"><a href="#cb5-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                       <span class="at">country =</span> <span class="st">&quot;Germany&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb5-4"><a href="#cb5-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                       <span class="at">region =</span> <span class="st">&quot;Bayern&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb5-5"><a href="#cb5-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                       <span class="at">daterange =</span> <span class="st">&quot;20210501-20210503&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb5-6"><a href="#cb5-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt;   data.percent_vu data.vu_se data.percent_vu_unw data.vu_se_unw</span></span>
<span id="cb5-7"><a href="#cb5-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 1        0.730857   0.030113            0.740484       0.025786</span></span>
